These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: broccoli, avocado, spinach, carrot
Nationality: colombian, canadian, indian, argentine
1. Nationality:canadian is on the left of Nationality:colombian##1
2. Food:broccoli == Nationality:argentine##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Nationality:colombian##1
4. Food:avocado is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1
5. Food:carrot is on the left of Nationality:colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | carrot | spinach | avocado | broccoli   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | colombian     | indian   | argentine |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: baking, writing, chess, skydiving
Sport: biathlon, golf, baseball, rowing
1. Hobby:skydiving == Sport:golf##1
2. Hobby:baking is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:writing is on the right of Hobby:skydiving##1
4. Hobby:skydiving is on the right of Sport:baseball##1
5. Sport:golf is on the left of Sport:biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | chess | skydiving | writing | baking    |
| Sport   | baseball    | golf      | biathlon | rowing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Hobby: filmmaking, chess, hiking, skydiving
Movie-Genre: musical, horror, comedy, spy
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left of Movie-Genre:spy##1
2. Hobby:filmmaking == Movie-Genre:musical##1
3. Movie-Genre:horror is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:spy is on the right of Hobby:skydiving##1
5. Hobby:hiking is on the left of Movie-Genre:horror##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving | hiking   | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | comedy | spy | horror         |

