3. Beverage:cola is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
4. Beverage:mirinda is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:7up == Music-Genre:trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | 7up  | lemonade | cola |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | trance | dubstep           | metal   |

